-- K+S May Switch to Registered Shares, Financial Times Deutschland Reports
-- B y   J u l i e   C r u z
-- 2010-11-15T06:11:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-15/k-s-may-switch-to-registered-shares-financial-times-deutschland-reports.html
K+S AG , a German potash producer,
may switch to registered shares, so as to have more information
about investors, the  Financial Times Deutschland  reported,
citing an unidentified company spokesman.  The change would be made after the May annual shareholders
meeting, at the earliest, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
 Julie Cruz  in Frankfurt at 
 jcruz6@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
David Merritt at 
 dmerritt1@bloomberg.net . 